I hear the roar of a big machine\
Two worlds and in between\
Hot metal and methedrine\
I hear empire down\
I hear empire down

I hear the roar of a big machine\
Two worlds and in between\
Love lost, fire at will\
Dum-dum bullets and shoot to kill, I hear\
Dive, bombers, and\
Empire down\
Empire down
